Module it.unipr.shopfx
Package it.unipr.warehouse

Class Order

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.warehouse.Product
it.unipr.warehouse.Order
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Product>
public class Order extends Product
The Order class, extension of the Product class, defines an order object:

An instance of Object contains all the data that identifies an order itself, you can set or get any of its attributes and also print it in its own format
